{"tid":2047643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【離婚剖白｜為婚外情認錯】暗示同魏駿傑六年冇夫妻性生活 張利華：我同佢都痛苦","createTime":"2020-06-02T08:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T04:14:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5e95f8fd6243df26ab1512527c3fd0b54807aa8d","tid":2047643,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"離婚後剖白<br />\n52歲魏駿傑與重慶嫩妻張利華的婚姻，隨住2015年被揭現裂痕，自始屢傳婚變。直至今年初本刊發現仍是人妻的她，與外籍Banker交往，她跟魏駿傑十二年的婚姻正式劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\n今日脫下人妻包袱，重新開始，張利華決心剖白：「我諗咗好耐，覺得應該要正面去面對問題，而且咁多年嚟嘅報道，有啲事實被扭曲咗。」<br />\n<br />\n婚姻破裂，她強調：「一隻手掌係拍唔響。」言下之意，不是她一個人的錯，魏駿傑都要負責任。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200601/1536pix/1591012003_b0bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200601%2F1536pix%2F1591012003_b0bb.jpg&h=0bdfd237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_743101_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_743101_0&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesber6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=dc18ef78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_743101_0&h=bd088558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_743101_0</a>"},{"pid":"43baeb376c1884d663c6ab7e93a7bfef2cc8b5e0","tid":2047643,"uid":171786,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰，我都唔屌你啦"},{"pid":"11e2713e92fa92a2435ac23ac54abc7a877f69f0","tid":2047643,"uid":51701,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"本身個肥佬性無格先搵隻大陸雞(可能)"},{"pid":"f09179c86c3bdfe34cfcad9003326e2ec0206e92","tid":2047643,"uid":38757,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"佢個咩樣黎...整到想嘔喎"},{"pid":"119af9e04e17b1a11fbdd78c37cc3bc3cf25613c","tid":2047643,"uid":124277,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":2,